English
You are required to design a Library Management Program.
The system should allow the librarian to:

Add a new book by entering the title, author, publication year, unique book ID, and status (default is "available" if not entered).

Display all books currently stored in the system, showing all details (ID, title, author, year, status).

Search for a book in three ways:

By Book ID

By Book Title

By Book Status ("available" or "borrowed")

Exit the program when finished.

The program should keep running until the user chooses to exit.
